# Project Context

This is an Opik demo project for client demonstrations. It uses:
- Python 3.12+ with Poetry for dependency management
- Anthropic Claude (claude-sonnet-4-5) as the LLM provider
- Opik for LLM observability and tracing

## Project Structure

- `app.py` - Main application entrypoint
- `config.yml` - Model parameters and project settings (non-secrets)
- `.env` - API keys and secrets (from `.env.example`)
- `src/customer_support_agent/` - Package source code
- `src/customer_support_agent/utils/config.py` - Unified config loader

## Common Commands

- `make setup` - Install dependencies and pre-commit hooks
- `make run` - Run the application
- `make test` - Run tests
- `make format` - Format code with ruff
- `make lint` - Check code with ruff
